Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来怎么结尾阿鲁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨啊  这还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼啊~地再开了  当然也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼啊~地闭幕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么各位
